pmn01a-data-displayed-survey: Lintlha tse hlahang deshebotong ena li bokelloa ka kotloloho ho tsoa likarabong tsa lipatlisiso 'me ha li tsoe ho lipalo-palo tsa naha kapa lisebelisoa tsa data. E emela maikutlo a hlahisitsoeng ke bacha nakong ea lipatlisiso, 'me liqeto leha e le life tse nkiloeng ho tsoa likarabong tsena ke boikarabelo ba mosebedisi, eseng PMNCH. PMNCH e ikemiseditse ho hlompha, ho kgothaletsa le ho sireletsa ditokelo le boiketlo ba batho bohle. Maikutlo afe kapa afe a hlahisitsoeng likarabong tsa lipatlisiso kapa lingoliloeng tse hatisitsoeng tse hlahang deshebotong ena tse hananang le boitlamo bona ha li amoheloe ke PMNCH.
